{"tid":1166273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指控陳浩民、馬德鐘非禮 陳嘉桓素顏報警","createTime":"2019-05-22T10:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T11:26:27.000Z","uid":11148,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe57bafc77eaa0b0fc14e99bb08d98c04d0e907","tid":1166273,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:25:17.000Z","msg":"19歲影圈新人陳嘉桓（Rose）於上周六（19日）深夜，在橫店拍攝王晶新片《笑功震武林》後，與一班香港演員洪天明、馬德鐘、陳浩民及幕後人員等，到當地一間串燒店食消夜期間，疑被帶醉意的<span style=\"color: red;\">陳浩民及馬德鐘手口並用輪流「抽水」和強吻</span>。事件引起關注，昨日下午3時，陳嘉桓在律師及經理人Ronnie（陳菀思）陪同下在觀塘寫字樓舉行記者會，陳嘉桓不施脂粉，一臉疲態，全程心情沉重及不時眼泛淚光。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20111123/15826876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20111123%2F15826876&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=577a86f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20111123%2F15826876&h=e667b404\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20111123/15826876</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/204408_584e44e5eb5c2842f691e1b069a92907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F204408_584e44e5eb5c2842f691e1b069a92907.jpg&h=2dfcf4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/204443_0a2c0a74bf136351004df83b7132362a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F204443_0a2c0a74bf136351004df83b7132362a.jpg&h=3dd720af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/204510_dab3462d4319063b1946b24253702117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F204510_dab3462d4319063b1946b24253702117.jpg&h=cd31e2ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/204544_1efd56c7b61f0dc8cd7635e22b58ef9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F204544_1efd56c7b61f0dc8cd7635e22b58ef9f.jpg&h=5cdc50b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「當時我好驚好亂」<br />\n經理人Ronnie對今次事件表示震驚，指是一項非常嚴重的非禮刑事案，令中、港、台演藝界蒙羞。記者會後陳嘉桓直接往觀塘警署報案，逗留了個半小時後，轉往將軍澳警署再落口供，陳嘉桓的律師透露正與內地律師商討是否有需要再到浙江報警。<br />\n警方發言人表示，昨日接獲一名19歲少女報案，聲稱較早前在內地被非禮，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方將案件列「境外罪案」處理</span>。<br />\n陳嘉桓昨在記者會上，多次顯得不知所措，不時唞大氣，數度硬咽。她表示到橫店拍該片才認識陳浩民及馬德鐘，洪天明叫她與劇組的香港演員一起吃飯，直至洪天明酩酊大醉後事件就發生。她說：「當時好驚，唔知點算，冇諗過印象中兩位演藝界前輩，各自又有幸福家庭，而自己又咁細個，我覺得佢哋兩個只係當我係小妹妹看待，冇諗過佢哋突然之間變咗另一個人。因為當時情況我好驚、好亂，未及作出反應&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n陳嘉桓承認今次事件自己警覺性不足，記者問她事發時可有作出行為或語言上反抗？她點頭，並說：「當時有反抗，初頭因為相信佢哋，少咗戒心，少咗警覺性。」經理人亦表示當時她曾推開對方。<br />\n或考慮往浙江報警<br />\n陳嘉桓的代表律師表示要報案後，再由香港警方決定誰是證人及被告。律師表示雖然今次事件是在境外發生，但以香港人普通法可以在香港報案，但在搜證上會有些問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">他會向內地律師諮詢法律意見，或會考慮去浙江報警。由於抽水事件發生在內地，礙於兩地的司法管轄權，要在香港審理案件會遇上一定難度，但只要人證和物證充足，同樣可按照一般司法程序審理。假若辯方要求在內地開審，亦有可能會移交內地司法機關辦理。根據內地刑法，這類屬於涉嫌「強制猥褻」及「侮辱婦女」，一旦罪成，最高可被判處五年以上有期徒刑</span>。<br />\n據悉陳浩民昨日已秘密返港，直接返抵北角寓所。<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例一通過咁咪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0517ec52cefff48c5e125d379b78795511cb6a","tid":1166273,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"又有兩個壞咗嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5194168a558f5be7d33f5d45946e5f914f6c0c1c","tid":1166273,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"2011年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41d7427c996f72dda7a636f236f61e84cd7b501","tid":1166273,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20110611/large/11ec2p20n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20110611%2Flarge%2F11ec2p20n.jpg&h=ddd428f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6978fc79d4de899722c7bc98fd882595298437c6","tid":1166273,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5194168a558f5be7d33f5d45946e5f914f6c0c1c","tid":1166273,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"2011年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"條例過咗就會有追溯期"},{"pid":"ded9aa44aae29bc951e9b1f6e48e16ee799a0736","tid":1166273,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a41d7427c996f72dda7a636f236f61e84cd7b501","tid":1166273,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20110611/large/11ec2p20n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20110611%2Flarge%2F11ec2p20n.jpg&h=ddd428f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"女人，俾人開發過就乜撚都唔驚<br />\n最驚係你冇錢又要屌"}]}